==English==

===Noun===
'''winch''' ([[winches]])
* A machine consisting of a [[drum]] on an [[axle]], a [[pawl]], and a [[crank]] [[handle]], with or without [[gearing]], to give increased [[mechanical advantage]] when [[haul]]ing on a [[rope]].

